            morality. Set on the battlefield of Kurukshetra, it provides
            insights into self-realization, the nature of existence, and the
            path to spiritual awakening. Renowned for its philosophical depth,
            the Gita remains a source of inspiration, guiding individuals
            through life's dilemmas and offering a profound understanding of the
            self and the universe. Reading the Bhagavad Gita is a transformative
            journey, fostering spiritual growth and enlightenment.
