          guides one to navigate life with integrity, detachment from results,
          and a compassionate heart. The Gita instills the importance of inner
          peace, ethical conduct, and the pursuit of knowledge. Its teachings
          transcend time, offering profound insights into the nature of
          existence and the path to spiritual fulfillment.
        </p>
